import React from 'react';
import { Canvas } from '@react-three/fiber';
import { OrbitControls } from '@react-three/drei';
import * as THREE from 'three';

interface RobotPartProps {
  position?: [number, number, number];
  color: string;
  style: number;
}

const RobotHead: React.FC<RobotPartProps> = ({ position = [0, 2, 0], color, style }) => {
  const headGeometries = [
    // Style 1: Boxy head
    <mesh position={position} key="head1">
      <boxGeometry args={[1.2, 1, 1.2]} />
      <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      <mesh position={[0.3, 0, 0.61]}>
        <sphereGeometry args={[0.2, 16, 16]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" />
      </mesh>
      <mesh position={[-0.3, 0, 0.61]}>
        <sphereGeometry args={[0.2, 16, 16]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" />
      </mesh>
    </mesh>,
    
    // Style 2: Rounded head
    <mesh position={position} key="head2">
      <sphereGeometry args={[0.7, 32, 32]} />
      <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      <mesh position={[0.3, 0, 0.5]} rotation={[0, 0, 0]}>
        <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.2, 0.1, 16]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" />
      </mesh>
      <mesh position={[-0.3, 0, 0.5]} rotation={[0, 0, 0]}>
        <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.2, 0.1, 16]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" />
      </mesh>
    </mesh>,
    
    // Style 3: Cyber head
    <mesh position={position} key="head3">
      <cylinderGeometry args={[0.8, 0.6, 1, 6]} />
      <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      <mesh position={[0.4, 0, 0.4]} rotation={[0, 0, 0]}>
        <boxGeometry args={[0.3, 0.1, 0.1]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" emissive="#4fc3f7" emissiveIntensity={0.5} />
      </mesh>
      <mesh position={[-0.4, 0, 0.4]} rotation={[0, 0, 0]}>
        <boxGeometry args={[0.3, 0.1, 0.1]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" emissive="#4fc3f7" emissiveIntensity={0.5} />
      </mesh>
    </mesh>
  ];

  return headGeometries[style - 1];
};

const RobotBody: React.FC<RobotPartProps> = ({ position = [0, 0, 0], color, style }) => {
  const bodyGeometries = [
    // Style 1: Standard body
    <mesh position={position} key="body1">
      <boxGeometry args={[2, 2.5, 1]} />
      <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      <mesh position={[0, 0, 0.51]}>
        <circleGeometry args={[0.5, 32]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" />
      </mesh>
    </mesh>,
    
    // Style 2: Rounded body
    <mesh position={position} key="body2">
      <cylinderGeometry args={[1.2, 1, 2.5, 32]} />
      <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      <mesh position={[0, 0, 1]}>
        <torusGeometry args={[0.3, 0.1, 16, 32]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" emissive="#4fc3f7" emissiveIntensity={0.5} />
      </mesh>
    </mesh>,
    
    // Style 3: Angular body
    <mesh position={position} key="body3">
      <cylinderGeometry args={[1, 1.5, 2.5, 8]} />
      <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      <mesh position={[0, 0, 1]}>
        <boxGeometry args={[1, 1, 0.1]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" metalness={0.8} roughness={0.2} />
      </mesh>
    </mesh>
  ];

  return bodyGeometries[style - 1];
};

const RobotArms: React.FC<RobotPartProps> = ({ position = [0, 0, 0], color, style }) => {
  const armGeometries = [
    // Style 1: Simple arms
    <group position={position} key="arms1">
      <mesh position={[1.5, 0, 0]}>
        <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.2, 2]} rotation={[0, 0, Math.PI / 2]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      </mesh>
      <mesh position={[-1.5, 0, 0]}>
        <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.2, 2]} rotation={[0, 0, Math.PI / 2]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      </mesh>
    </group>,
    
    // Style 2: Jointed arms
    <group position={position} key="arms2">
      <group position={[1.2, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <sphereGeometry args={[0.3, 16, 16]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[0.8, -0.4, 0]} rotation={[0, 0, -Math.PI / 4]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.15, 1.2]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
      <group position={[-1.2, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <sphereGeometry args={[0.3, 16, 16]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[-0.8, -0.4, 0]} rotation={[0, 0, Math.PI / 4]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.15, 1.2]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
    </group>,
    
    // Style 3: Robotic arms
    <group position={position} key="arms3">
      <group position={[1.2, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <boxGeometry args={[0.4, 0.4, 0.4]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[0.6, 0, 0]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.2, 1]} rotation={[0, 0, Math.PI / 2]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" metalness={0.8} roughness={0.2} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
      <group position={[-1.2, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <boxGeometry args={[0.4, 0.4, 0.4]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[-0.6, 0, 0]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.2, 1]} rotation={[0, 0, Math.PI / 2]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" metalness={0.8} roughness={0.2} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
    </group>
  ];

  return armGeometries[style - 1];
};

const RobotLegs: React.FC<RobotPartProps> = ({ position = [0, -2, 0], color, style }) => {
  const legGeometries = [
    // Style 1: Simple legs
    <group position={position} key="legs1">
      <mesh position={[0.5, 0, 0]}>
        <cylinderGeometry args={[0.25, 0.25, 2]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      </mesh>
      <mesh position={[-0.5, 0, 0]}>
        <cylinderGeometry args={[0.25, 0.25, 2]} />
        <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
      </mesh>
    </group>,
    
    // Style 2: Jointed legs
    <group position={position} key="legs2">
      <group position={[0.5, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.3, 0.2, 1]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[0, -0.8, 0.2]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.3, 1]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
      <group position={[-0.5, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.3, 0.2, 1]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[0, -0.8, 0.2]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.2, 0.3, 1]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
    </group>,
    
    // Style 3: Robotic legs
    <group position={position} key="legs3">
      <group position={[0.5, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <boxGeometry args={[0.4, 1, 0.4]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[0, -0.8, 0]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.3, 0.3, 1]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" metalness={0.8} roughness={0.2} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
      <group position={[-0.5, 0, 0]}>
        <mesh>
          <boxGeometry args={[0.4, 1, 0.4]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color={color} />
        </mesh>
        <mesh position={[0, -0.8, 0]}>
          <cylinderGeometry args={[0.3, 0.3, 1]} />
          <meshStandardMaterial color="#4fc3f7" metalness={0.8} roughness={0.2} />
        </mesh>
      </group>
    </group>
  ];

  return legGeometries[style - 1];
};

interface Robot3DProps {
  parts: {
    head: number;
    body: number;
    arms: number;
    legs: number;
    color: string;
  };
}

const Robot3D: React.FC<Robot3DProps> = ({ parts }) => {
  return (
    <Canvas camera={{ position: [0, 0, 10], fov: 50 }}>
      <ambientLight intensity={0.5} />
      <pointLight position={[10, 10, 10]} intensity={0.5} />
      <pointLight position={[-10, -10, -10]} intensity={0.2} />
      
      <group rotation={[0, Math.PI / 4, 0]}>
        <RobotHead color={parts.color} style={parts.head} />
        <RobotBody color={parts.color} style={parts.body} />
        <RobotArms color={parts.color} style={parts.arms} />
        <RobotLegs color={parts.color} style={parts.legs} />
      </group>
      
      <OrbitControls enableZoom={true} enablePan={false} />
      <gridHelper args={[20, 20, "#4fc3f7", "#4fc3f7"]} position={[0, -3, 0]} />
    </Canvas>
  );
};

export default Robot3D;
